                            <span>고정밀 3D 스캔</span>
                            <span>족압 분석</span>
                            <span>보행 패턴 검사</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="step-image">
                        <img src="/images/step1-scan.jpg" alt="족압 측정 과정" loading="lazy">
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="process-step reverse" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="200">
